Package com.b2international.snowowl.datastore.oplock.impl

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDatastoreOperationLockManager
    Marker interface for pinning the type parameter of IOperationLockManager.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractDatastoreLockTarget
    Common superclass of all lock targets for terminology stores.
    AllRepositoriesLockTarget
    A lock target which represents the a single terminology store.
    DatastoreLockContext
    Represents a lock context carrying a user identifier and a message describing the operation for which the lock is to be acquired.
    DatastoreLockContextDescriptions
    Contains context descriptions used in DatastoreLockContexts.
    DatastoreLockManagerClientConfigJob
    The client-side service initialization job for the datastore operation lock manager.
    SingleRepositoryAndBranchLockTarget
    A lock target referring to a single repository branch by the unique identifier of the repository and the branch path.
    SingleRepositoryLockTarget
    A lock target referring to a single repository by its unique identifier.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DatastoreOperationLockException
    Thrown when reporting issues related to locking any terminology store.
